                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah_lw &amp;lt;wei3.liu@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/e8a20d7a-250e-11e5-bf7b-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/e8a20d7a-250e-11e5-bf7b-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_36 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Migrate inode user limit failed: 3
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;test log&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Copy admin quota files into MDT0...
CMD: shadow-14vm4 test -b ldiskfs
shadow-14vm4, /dev/lvm-Role_MDS/P1, /mnt/mds1, -o loop
CMD: shadow-14vm4 mount -t ldiskfs -o loop /dev/lvm-Role_MDS/P1 /mnt/mds1
CMD: shadow-14vm4 mkdir /mnt/mds1/OBJECTS
CMD: shadow-14vm4 cp /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/admin_quotafile_v2.usr /mnt/mds1/OBJECTS
shadow-14vm4: cp: cannot stat `/usr/lib64/lustre/tests/admin_quotafile_v2.usr&apos;: No such file or directory
CMD: shadow-14vm4 cp /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/admin_quotafile_v2.grp /mnt/mds1/OBJECTS
shadow-14vm4: cp: cannot stat `/usr/lib64/lustre/tests/admin_quotafile_v2.grp&apos;: No such file or directory
CMD: shadow-14vm4 umount -d -f /mnt/mds1
Setup all...
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
